OL,3,CTrio first to be jailed on violent
OL,4,Cdisorder charge after nationwide riots
OL,6,FThree men have been jailed for violent
OL,7,Fdisorder after disturbances which
OL,8,Fbroke out following the stabbing of
OL,9,Fthree girls at a Taylor Swift themed
OL,10,Fdance event in Southport.
OL,12,FThey are the first sentences for this
OL,13,Fcharge to be handed down after a
OL,14,Fseries of demonstrations across the
OL,15,FUK, with the judge hoping it would act
OL,16,Fas a "deterrent".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/16
