OL,4,Cdisorder charge after nationwide riots
OL,6,FSenior district crown prosecutor
OL,7,FJonathan Egan said the sentences were
OL,8,F"the tip of the iceberg, and just the
OL,9,Fstart of what will be a very painful
OL,10,Fprocess for many who foolishly chose
OL,11,Fto involve themselves in violent
OL,12,Funrest".
OL,14,FHe added: "Many of those involved will
OL,15,Fbe sent to prison for a long time."
OL,17,FThe three men were each jailed when
OL,18,Fthey appeared at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,19,Fon 7 August.
