OL,6,FDerek Drummond, 58, from Pool Street
OL,7,Fin Southport, was handed three years
OL,8,Fin prison after he admitted punching a
OL,9,Fpolice officer outside Southport
OL,10,Fmosque on 30 July.
OL,12,FLiam Riley, 40 of Walton Road in
OL,13,FLiverpool, has been sentenced to 20
OL,14,Fmonths after he admitted violent
OL,15,Fdisorder and racially aggravated
OL,16,Fbehaviour - telling officers they
OL,17,Fwere, "traitors and Muslim lovers" -
OL,18,Fin Liverpool on 3 August.
