OL,3,CTrio first to be jailed on violent
OL,4,Cdisorder charge after nationwide riots
OL,6,FDeclan Geiran, 29, of Kelso Road in
OL,7,FLiverpool, who received 30 months in
OL,8,Fprison after he admitted using an
OL,9,F"implement" to set fire to a police
OL,10,Fvan in Liverpool on 3 August, and
OL,11,Fsending a malicious communication in
OL,12,F2023.
OL,14,FAll three men were due to appear at
OL,15,FLiverpool Crown Court later in August
OL,16,Fbut their cases were fast-tracked.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
