OL,6,FPassing sentence the Honorary Recorder
OL,7,Fof Liverpool, Judge Andrew Menary KC,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Quite simply those who
OL,9,Fdeliberately participate in such
OL,10,Fdisorder, causing injury, damage and
OL,11,Ffear to communities, will inevitably
OL,12,Fbe punished with sentences designed to
OL,13,Fdeter others from similar activity."
OL,15,FReferring to the disturbances near to
OL,16,FSouthport Mosque on 30 July following
OL,17,Fthe vigil in the town, he said: "The
OL,18,Fgenuine and collective grief of the
OL,19,Fresidents of Southport was effectively
OL,20,Fhijacked by this callous behaviour."
