OL,6,FThe court heard Gerian wrote off a
OL,7,Fpolice van after he set a seatbelt on
OL,8,Ffire while the vehicle was parked in
OL,9,FLiverpool city centre.
OL,11,FProsecutor Christopher Taylor told the
OL,12,Fcourt footage uploaded to TikTok
OL,13,Fshowed the defendant at the open
OL,14,Fwindow on the driver's side as he set
OL,15,Fthe seatbelt alight and smoke billowed
OL,16,Fout.
