OL,6,FGeiran remained at the scene and was
OL,7,Fseen to sit casually on the fountain
OL,8,Foutside the Walker Art Gallery and
OL,9,Fthen take out his phone to film the
OL,10,Fvan, he said.
OL,12,FHe was swiftly tracked on CCTV footage
OL,13,Fand arrested a short time later, the
OL,14,Fcourt heard.
OL,16,FWhen interviewed, he said attended the
OL,17,Fprotest at Pier Head alone and wanted
OL,18,Fto "show his support" for the bereaved
OL,19,Ffamilies of the three girls murdered
OL,20,Fin Southport.
