OL,6,FMr Taylor said: "He heard shouts of
OL,7,F'burn the van, burn the van' and
OL,8,Fstated he felt under pressure.
OL,10,F"He didn't believe his actions had
OL,11,Fcaused the damage."
OL,13,FThe Transit van was written off, said
OL,14,Fthe prosecutor, with new replacement
OL,15,Fvans costing more than #32,000.
