OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing of Gerian,
OL,7,FAssistant Chief Constable Paul White
OL,8,Fof Merseyside Police said: "Just four
OL,9,Fdays after trying to burn a police
OL,10,Fvan, Geiran has been driven in the
OL,11,Fback of a prison van to serve a 30-
OL,12,Fmonth term in jail.
OL,14,F"The message is clear: if you get
OL,15,Finvolved in disorder, don't count on
OL,16,Fending the week at home with your
OL,17,Ffamily."
