OL,6,FElsewhere a man has pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Finciting racial hatred by using racist
OL,8,Flanguage on a live stream he
OL,9,Fbroadcasted to "millions of people"
OL,10,Ffrom outside a hotel in Stockport
OL,11,Fthought to contain asylum seekers.
OL,13,FAaron Johnson, 32, of Criterion
OL,14,FStreet, North Reddish, pleaded guilty
OL,15,Fat Manchester Magistrates' Court to
OL,16,Fdistributing images intended to stir
OL,17,Fup racial hatred outside the hotel on
OL,18,FMonday 5 August.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@cO]
