OL,6,FProsecutor Laura Peers said: "Members
OL,7,Fof staff became aware of the defendant
OL,8,Flive streaming from his mobile phone
OL,9,Fonto YouTube."
OL,11,FMs Peers said Johnson "became
OL,12,Faggressive to members of staff" at the
OL,13,Fhotel, adding that he told them "he
OL,14,Fwould smash their face in".
OL,16,FThe prosecutor said Johnson, who was
OL,17,Farrested outside the hotel, had
OL,18,F"exposed occupants of the hotel to a
OL,19,Freal danger".
