OL,6,FShe said the live stream had been
OL,7,F"viewed by millions of people", adding
OL,8,F"within the stream he repeatedly
OL,9,Frefers to migrants in a derogatory
OL,10,Fmanner" and used racist language.
OL,12,FDistrict Judge Jane Hamilton told
OL,13,FJohnson: "You had no reason to attend
OL,14,Fthe hotel where you were live
OL,15,Fstreaming.
OL,17,F"You were taking pictures through the
OL,18,Fwindows where people were trying to
OL,19,Fsleep.
