OL,6,F"You also made reference to the
OL,7,Fchildren who were unfortunately
OL,8,Fmurdered in Southport ` that had
OL,9,Fnothing to do with asylum seekers or
OL,10,Fanything else.
OL,12,F"The man who did that was born in this
OL,13,Fcountry."
OL,15,FJohnson was remanded into custody and
