OL,6,FTwo men have also been charged with
OL,7,Fracially aggravated assaults and
OL,8,Fpublic order offences following
OL,9,Fprotests in Manchester at the weekend,
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police said.
OL,12,FMatthew Wilson, 31, repeatedly punched
OL,13,Fthe glass of the dock, shouted
OL,14,Fobscenities and put his middle finger
OL,15,Fup at a judge as he denied racially
OL,16,Faggravated assault and public order
OL,17,Foffences.
