OL,6,FHe appeared alongside Alex Fraser, 20,
OL,7,Fwho denied the same charge after they
OL,8,Fallegedly made racist comments and
OL,9,F"randomly" attacked an Asian man in
OL,10,FManchester city centre on Monday.
OL,12,FJulie Sweeney, 53, appeared at
OL,13,FWarrington Magistrates' Court but was
OL,14,Fnot required to enter a plea, after
OL,15,Fbeing charged with publishing written
OL,16,Fmaterial to stir up racial hatred.
OL,18,FShe is accused of allegedly posting a
OL,19,Fthreatening message suggesting to
OL,20,F"blow up a mosque with adults inside",
OL,21,Fa court official said.
