OL,6,FCourt papers allege that on Saturday,
OL,7,Fat Church Lawton, the defendant "sent
OL,8,Fa message that conveyed a threat of
OL,9,Fdeath or serious harm, namely,
OL,10,Fsuggesting to 'blow up a mosque with
OL,11,Fadults inside', intending, or being
OL,12,Freckless as to whether, an individual
OL,13,Fencountering the message would fear
OL,14,Fthat the threat would be carried out".
OL,16,FThe court appearances come as police
OL,17,Fremain braced for planned unrest by
OL,18,F"hateful and divisive groups" as they
OL,19,Fmonitor reports of at least 30
OL,20,Fpossible gatherings and threats
OL,21,Fagainst immigration law specialists.
